The locale_name filter returns the locale name given its two-letter code: <br>

{# German #}
{{ 'de'|locale_name }} <br>
By default, the filter uses the current locale. You can pass it explicitly: <br>

{# allemand #}
{{ 'de'|locale_name('fr') }} <br>

{# fran√ßais (Canada) #}
{{ 'fr_CA'|locale_name('fr_FR') }} <br>
